data.description: Welcome to this Amazing home with a 4 car garage!! Truly a rare find in Springfield! The home features large living room with LED lighting, an open kitchen, a large double stainless sink. New flooring thru-out the home was installed in 2022. A new water heater with 10 year warranty was installed in 2023. This Radiant floor home on slab foundation includes an outdoor shed, and a heated four car garage.
